        },
        {
          "name": "reply_challenge_1",
          "value": "Well done for trying the activity! When we listen to our teenagers, even if we disagree, we learn to understand their thinking. Try and find time to do the activity again - try to really listen and show you understand them before sharing your thoughts.",
          "_translations": {
            "value": {
