        },
        {
          "name": "reply_challenge_5",
          "value": "It is difficult to know every detail about our communities. Involve another family member or friend in your mapping activity. You can even visit some of the services available and ask what they do. The more we know, the better we can keep our families safe!",
          "_translations": {
            "value": {
              "tz_sw": true,
