        {
          "name": "reply_challenge_6",
          "value": "That's totally fine! You can still support your teen. Ask your teen to explain the gadgets they use - you could do this during one-on-one time. This is a great opportunity to show interest in your teen’s life and to discuss potential risks together. If you are not sure which rules to set, you can always agree, with your teen, to try a new rule for two weeks and then discuss how things are going and change the rule if needed!",
